        <div class="item discover">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="p">
                    <p>
	The Yukon Workers&rsquo; Compensation Health and Safety Board is funded solely by Yukon employers.Our job is preventing disability. We do that by providing compensation, service and support to Yukon workers injured on the job. We also promote workplace safety through training, inspection and compliance and investigations.</p>

                    <p class="action"><a class="button-b small" href="/LIB0061.aspx">Learn more...</a></p>
